      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BONNEVILLE (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and two minors from eight tries. In the money last time at this track (20.03) in a P5, finishing a 2 length third. Rates on top and should go close. ZIPPING DAYTONA (4) box seated off the lead and kept coming to win (19.66) at this track in Grade 5 over 366m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. SMOKY CHIPOTLE (7) is a promising dog in the frame at six of 13 starts including four wins and was in the minors again latest (30.51) over 520m at Q Parklands. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. BANORA BEACH (8) has won at this course and distance, cannot be underestimated.",
